            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Aumente o valor da variável <code>wallet</code> em um.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" wallet = \" /><text value=\"13\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"wallet++;\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(wallet);\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"17\" endIndex=\"23\" /><option startIndex=\"23\" endIndex=\"24\" /><option startIndex=\"24\" endIndex=\"25\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"wallet + 2\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"14\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>wallet</code> seguido de <code>+</code> e finalmente <code>+</code>.</p></body></html>"
